blog.name: swift-as-taylor
blog.title: Such Swift
blog.description:
Well Howdy! I'm Simone (aka Sim1 the first simulation, beep boop) I'm... you guessed it! over 12 (psst I'm 19 though I don't always act it) I have been a fan of the girl with the hella good hair (that's code for Taylor Swift incase you didn't know) for... well... let's just say a long time. I've had the honor of seeing her live on the Red Tour (rip it was the rain shortened show) The 1989 Tour, and soon the Reputiontion tour (peep me I'll be in

Kentucky June 30th,  Sec.FLDB2, Row 27, Seats 11-12

) Though I've never been graced by the awe inspiring presence of the true queen Taylor (in person or online) I have been blessed with a hug from the one and only Mama Swift (it was better than you think) Feel free to hit me up to talk about Taylor, Harry Potter, Grey's Anatomy, Supergirl, Percy Jackson, or to I dunno just talk (do people do that? I dunno I only mime) Anyway this is WAAAAY too long now so I'll just see myself out now.... bye I guess... (is it bye if you're still looking at my profile? Who knows?)

title: Love You Taylor Swift
body:
Look back to the past,you’ve been through so much rumor.
One years later,after the storm ,Reputation comes out all of a sudden
Victory in both love and music
Even We are so far away,we really concern you.
Though you don’t come to Taiwan this time,we will still love you forever.
Swift, We will be waiting for you .

@taylorswift
